Generic, wildcard, PECS, socket, thread, sleep, runnable

1. Write own scheduler task
   That helps to run some task periodically

2. Write synchronous chat between two machines (use ServerSocket and Socket)

3. Using Producer-Consumer pattern implement mechanism that will put candy into the Box if it's empty.
   Consumer look at the box only if he knows, that box not empty.
   Use wait and notify methods from Object.

4. Write universal downloader from ex.ua (That helps us download all files from page)
              1. First input url address of page
              2. then parse page and find urls like "/load/{idOfFile}" ex. href="/load/124701188"
              3. Take url and download file using URL class

5*. Try to implement asynchronous chat that allows communication with two and more users

6. install postgreSQL database